snippet.title: Eternity: The Last Unicorn - Launch Trailer | PC, PS4
snippet.description:
Pursuit of Eternity begins today! Eternity: The Last Unicorn is now avaliable on Steam and PS4:

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/714250/Eternity_The_Last_Unicorn/
PS4 (NA): https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP2769-CUSA08257_00-142030ETERNITY17

Platforms: PC and PS4 (Xbox One is coming later in 2019)

Eternity: The Last Unicorn is a classic RPG, with lore based on Norse mythology. Travel through mesmerizing locations, meet fantasy characters and fight to protect Elven immortality.

Follow us:
